name: The World Through MY Eyes - Kv7UxF2Lvx

metadata.name: The Apple Of My Eye
metadata.description:
The moment of realization that this is the person that makes my life complete and how my viewfinder focused on it perfectly. 
This will be 1/2 Special. A set of pictures that brings me down to life if I ever seem to forget my ways. 
Set in the brightest city in the world, Time Square, New York, yet she shined the brightest that night.
